      <section eId="sec_CE-1003">
        <num>CE 1003</num>
        <heading>1003. Â Admissibility of duplicates</heading>
        <subsection eId="CE-1003__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A genuine question is raised as to the authenticity of the original;</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CE-1003__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>In the circumstances it would be unfair to admit the duplicate in lieu of the original; or</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CE-1003__subsec_3">
          <num>(3)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The original is a testament offered for probate, a contract on which the claim or defense is based, or is otherwise closely related to a controlling issue.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=72429</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
